<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        fürgelegt Berhtold Deihsler und <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Lauginger,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, von iren und <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gesellschaft wegen, auch <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz in ewr amptleute ir hab und
                        kauffmanschaft <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und gen Wald gefürt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Darümb so
                            <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></add>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Pillsach<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>weis<ex>er</ex></expan> dicz briefs,
                        mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden davon
                            <expan>czurede<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz, waz etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. <app>
<note place="marginleft">Non sunt
                                <expan>p<ex>raese</ex>ntate</expan>.</note>
</app></ab>
</div>
